Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎其他所有的基础设施\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}virtually all other infrastructures
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.88,0:40:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会立刻失效  或在几天内失效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will fail either immediately or within just a few days.
