Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就喝不到饮用水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're not gonna have drinking water.
