Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.71,0:40:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须重建所有的变压器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They will have to be completely replayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.36,0:40:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是什么简单事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that is not a simple proposition.
