Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.93,0:41:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着  在六个月内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That means no electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.81,0:41:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大城市将陷入\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no water, no fuel, no banking
