Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.28,0:41:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而小城市要经历的时间则更长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Smaller cities will take longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.51,0:41:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重建一个完整的电网则需要十年以上的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To rebuild the entire grid might take over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.21,0:41:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复费用高得难以置信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cost of repair is staggering.
