Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.52,0:41:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是1亿美国人  2亿5千万欧洲人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's 100 million deaths in the U.S., 250 million in Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.84,0:42:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和10亿亚洲人死于一场磁暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A billion in Asia, lives lost to the power of a magnetic storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.01,0:42:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up until this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.49,0:42:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对这种灾难也没有一个清晰的认识\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}this sort of disaster has truly been incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.00,0:42:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做些什么  阻止这场灾难吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can anything be done to prevent this type of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.36,0:42:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专家们已经开始行动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Experts are trying to plan for that now,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.58,0:42:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对太阳表面的磁暴进行更细致的观察\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with better observation of the Sun's explosive magnetic surface,
