Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.05,0:42:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并为变压器设立强电振荡防护器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and creating surge preventers for transformers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.43,0:42:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我们必须想办法在电网的设计上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We now have to think in ways of retrofitting design changes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.05,0:42:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一些改进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into those grids.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.95,0:42:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于如何加强这些设施的防护\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're still at early days of trying to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.97,0:42:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍处于起步阶段\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how to harden the infrastructures against these.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.62,0:42:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁暴无与伦比的威力揭示了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The apocalyptic power of a magnetic storm reveals
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.61,0:42:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁是多么普遍而深远地影响了我们的生活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just how essential magnetism is in our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.88,0:42:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃至整个宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and in the very universe itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁是如此重要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Electromagnetism is the most important thing
