Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.87,0:43:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像水里的鱼不会在意水一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it's kind of like a fish in water doesn't think about water.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.91,0:43:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它无处不在  聚合世间万物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's everywhere. It holds everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.87,0:43:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气因磁而生  呼吸因磁而发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It holds the atmosphere, the action of breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.28,0:43:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛看见事物的过程是一种电磁交互\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the action of seeing is an electromagnetic interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.06,0:43:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁力是一种简单的力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Magnetism is a simple force,
