Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们的分子聚集在一起  幸运的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it holds our molecules together, and if we're lucky,
