Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于地球上的居民来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the inhabitants of Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.49,0:43:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是宇宙间最被我们忽视的力之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is one of the most overlooked forces in our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.82,0:43:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一切  都任其主宰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yet magnetism gives and can take everything.
